            <title>[PIG-1799] Provide deployable maven artifacts for pigunit and pig smoke tests</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-1799</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Having maven artifacts for pigunit framework and smoke test will help to separate execution of smoke tests against a physical cluster from a source tree (ant build),&lt;/p&gt;</description>
